  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your Sealed beasts' instincts becomes your own. You instinctually know where attacks come from almost as if you had a 6th sense for these things. Once per round, when you would be hit with an attack, you may spend 1 Twisted Chakra to increase your AC by 1, up to the difference between your AC and the rolled attack +1, against that attack. If the attack was a critical Hit, if you raise your AC to an amount equal to the Critical hits result +5, you treat it as a miss.</p>",
